                <p>With improved safety features, a host of driver assistance systems, and the latest version of BMW’s iDrive technology, the new X3 aims to set a benchmark in the premium SUV segment. The launch at Bharat Mobility Global Expo is poised to attract considerable attention, marking BMW’s continued focus on innovation and customer satisfaction in India.</p>
